Package: consortflow
Title: Sequential Exclusion Flowcharts for Observational Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-03-11
Authors@R: person("Timothy P", "Copeland", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "timothy.copeland@ki.se")
Description: Create publication-ready CONSORT-style exclusion flowcharts for
    observational studies. Provides a pipe-friendly API to sequentially exclude
    observations from a data frame while tracking counts, then render the
    exclusion flow as an auto-sizing diagram with labeled boxes and arrows.
    Uses R's built-in grid graphics — no Python or external rendering
    dependencies required.
